title: Readout from a Treasury Spokesperson of Secretary Lew’s Meeting with Brazil Finance Minister Joaquim Levy ...
text: ( Source : US Department of the Treasury ) LIMA - U.S. Treasury Secretary Jacob J. Lew met today with Brazil Finance Minister Joaquim Levy on the sidelines of the Annual Meetings of the International Monetary Fund ( IMF ) and the World Bank
